<h2>myriad.social</h2>
<p><p>"<i>a social network where i'm not blocked...yet</i>" - <a href="https://myriad.social/@Dre2Dee2">@Dre2Dee2</a></p>

<p>myriad.social is a discrete node in the <a href="https://medium.com/@Gargron/welcome-to-mastodon-111d9227e56a">mastodon</a> network and the <a href="https://gnu.io/social/">gnu social</a>-compliant <a href="https://www.fediverse.org/">fediverse</a>.</p>

<p>myriad.social is hosted in bucharest, romania and operates as a 'free-speech friendly' instance with emphasis on low moderation, high security, and full transparency, and operates under the auspices of <a href="http://patreon.com/myriadtruths">the myriad truths project.</a></p></p>
