<div class='panel'><p>myriad.social has a 'low-moderation' policy to facilitate free speech on this instance. This is not a legally binding document and may be updated and changed at our discretion, but currently our policy is to only remove content if it:</p>

<p> - depicts minors in a sexually explicit manner</p>
<p> - is illegal in romania (the locale where our infastructure resides)</p>
<p> - disrupts the stability of the instance for other users</p>

<p>please report any content which violates one of these directives. general security-related correspondence, such as vulnerability disclosures, are gladly received at <a href="mailto:security@myriad.social">security@myriad.social</a>.</p>

<p>myriad.social is a venture of <a href="https://patreon.com/myriadtruths">The Myriad Truths Project</a>, which accepts financial contributions from individual supporters and backers.</p></div>
